      "name": "Worst-case hemolysis operating condition claim",
      "description": "The CFD model correctly identifies the worst-case hemolysis operating condition among the five evaluated flow-speed combinations for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions, yielding a relative hemolysis index below 1.0 for all configurations assessed."
