    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index remains below 1.0 across all five operating points, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The claim that the model correctly identifies worst-case conditions is supported by the validation evidence on file.",
